reviewText: Excellent work! The team was professional, on time, and did a great job with our roof replacement. Highly recommend!
responseText: Thank you for your kind words, John! We're so glad you're happy with your new roof.

reviewText: Good service overall. The work was completed on schedule and the roof looks great. Minor communication issues but resolved quickly.
Outstanding quality and service. They handled everything from permits to cleanup. Very satisfied!
